column30:
IELTS: 6.0 overall or above (academic module) with a minimum of 5.0 in each component. 
TOEFL-iBT:75 or above with a minimum of 15 in Reading, Listening, Speaking and Writing. Cambridge Certificate in Advanced English (CAE): 170or above Duolingo: 100 or above

Submission of IB, A-level or other international standardized test score reports can exempt the applicantfrom providing English proficiency certificate .

Other requirements : Applicants must have scored 70% or above in Math, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology (Zoology & Botany)during high school.

column22:
There are three rates for tuition fee waivers:

A - 200,000 RMB waiver/year for 4 years (full fee waiver of all tuition fees)

B - 140,000 RMB waiver/year for 4 years (student contribution 60,000 RMB/year)

C - 80,000 RMB waiver/year for 4 years (student contribution 120,000 RMB/year)

D - 40,000 RMB waiver/year for 4 years (student contribution 160,000 RMB/year)

Academic Scholarship and Overseas Scholarship will be awarded during University study.

Duration: 4 years (The scholarship will be reviewed and given on the condition that the student meets the requirements for satisfactory progress toward a degree and follows the rules of the ZJU-UoE Institute.)

column30:
IELTS Academic: total 6.5 with at least 6.0 in each component. We do not accept IELTS One Skill Retake to meet our English language requirements.  
TOEFL-iBT (including Home Edition): total 92 with at least 23 in each component. We do not accept TOEFL MyBest Score to meet our English language requirements.
C1 Advanced (CAE) / C2 Proficiency (CPE): total 176 with at least 169 in each component.
Trinity ISE: ISE II with distinctions in all four components.
Oxford ELLT: total 7 with at least 6 in each component.
Oxford Test of English Advanced: total 145 with at least 135 in each component 
Other requirements : Biology and chemistry must have been taken as compulsory subjects in high school.

column20:
Two types of On-campus dormitory: CNY 15/day or 30/day.

BUILDING 17 OF LIUYUAN (BUILDING 17 PARK OF WILLOW):
For students of short term non-degree programs, the Price and Types of Room:
Single-bed room: RMB 21900/Year(The cost of water and Electricity are included)
Double-bed room: RMB 10950/Year(The cost of water and Electricity are included)

BUILDING 12 OF SONGUAN (BUILDING 12 PARK OF PINE): 
For male  students of degree programs, the Price and Types of Room:
Single-bed room: RMB 10950/Year (The partial cost of water and Electricity are  included)
Double-bed room: RMB 5500/Year (The partial cost of water and Electricity are  included)

BUILDING 2 OF HEYUAN (BUILDING 2 PARK OF LOTUS): 
For female  students of degree programs, the Price and Types of Room:
Single-bed room: RMB 10950/Year (The partial cost of water and Electricity are  included)
Double-bed room: RMB 5500/Year (The partial cost of water and Electricity are  included)

INTERNATIONAL STUDENT HOSTEL (BUILDING IN EAST CAMPUS): 
For postgradute and late stage of undergraduate students of medical programs, the Price and Types of Room:
Single-bed room: RMB 21900/Year (The partial cost of water and Electricity are  included)
Double-bed room: RMB 10950/Year (The partial cost of water and Electricity are  included)

Postgraduate students as well as undergraduate students (at Clinical Stage) can choose to dwell off campus.
column30: If the overall GPA of a Moroccan student in high school is below 14 points, they must first apply for our preparatory course. If the student does not obtain the final graduation certificate, they can apply for the undergraduate program only after obtaining the final graduation certificate and transcript. Students who have not obtained the graduation certificate should first apply for the preparatory course, or apply after obtaining the final documents, but there may not be any available seats. Meanwhile, students applying directly for the undergraduate program must submit the CSCA scores.
